{{version031}}
{{flavour|Blasts a targeted enemy with lightning, with no direct line of fire required. The targeting magics need distance to function, so enemies that are adjacent or nearly adjacent cannot be struck by this.}}

'''Call Down Lightning''' is a monster-only spell which deals electricity damage at range. It is [[smite-targeted]], however it cannot target creatures that are 2 tiles away or closer. Note that this spell can miss.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Call Down Lightning was added in [[0.27]].

[[Category: Monster spells]]
